          "activation_name": "Calistria\u2019s Sting",
          "effect": "Poison wells up from the armor\u2019s links to seep into the triggering creature\u2019s body, causing it to suffer wracking pains as if it was being stung by thousands of angry wasps. The triggering creature takes 7d6 persistent poison damage (DC 34 basic Fortitude save); this persistent damage can\u2019t be ended as long as the triggering creature continues to grapple you. *Slithermaw\u2019s Bane* can\u2019t activate Calistria\u2019s Sting using his actions.",
