    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "The heroism of Kyloss Syndar, founder of Greengold and slayer of the demonic hydra Slithermaw, imprinted this suit of armor with a gleaming, prismatic sheen that sparkles under bright light. The telepathic voice of *Slithermaw\u2019s Bane* is boisterous and grandiose, encouraging his partner to take up leadership roles while also providing advice to maintain loyalty and strengthen bonds of friendship.   \n  \n*Slithermaw\u2019s Bane* is a suit of *+3 major resilient greater fortification high-grade elven chain* that grants his wearer poison resistance 15, and the item bonus his resilient rune grants to saving throws versus poison increases by 1 to +4.",
    "traits": [
      {
        "alternate_link": {
